### =====================================================
### Appraisal Comparable - API Test File
### =====================================================
### Links/unlinks market comparables to appraisals
### =====================================================

@appraisalId = 019c813e-bd45-7fc4-9695-ce9d3ce064ab
@marketComparableId = 019C74DF-98DB-77BD-9F1C-7F5BB8F99B40
@comparableId = 019C8B50-39D6-75E0-B46C-9557EB0C7E15

### =====================================================
### 1. LINK COMPARABLE TO APPRAISAL
### =====================================================

### 1.1 Link Comparable 1
POST {{baseUrl}}/appraisals/{{appraisalId}}/comparables
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "marketComparableId": "{{marketComparableId}}",
  "sequenceNumber": 1,
  "originalPricePerUnit": 42000.00,
  "weight": 35.00,
  "selectionReason": "Closest proximity and similar land use",
  "notes": "Located within 500m of subject property"
}

### 1.2 Link Comparable 2
@marketComparableId2 = 019C74DF-98DB-77BD-9F1C-7F5BB8F99B40
POST {{baseUrl}}/appraisals/{{appraisalId}}/comparables
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "marketComparableId": "{{marketComparableId2}}",
  "sequenceNumber": 2,
  "originalPricePerUnit": 38000.00,
  "weight": 35.00,
  "selectionReason": "Similar lot size and shape"
}

### 1.3 Link Comparable 3
@marketComparableId3 = 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000003
POST {{baseUrl}}/appraisals/{{appraisalId}}/comparables
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "marketComparableId": "{{marketComparableId3}}",
  "sequenceNumber": 3,
  "originalPricePerUnit": 45000.00,
  "weight": 30.00
}

### =====================================================
### 2. GET APPRAISAL COMPARABLES
### =====================================================

### 2.1 Get all comparables for an appraisal
GET {{baseUrl}}/appraisals/{{appraisalId}}/comparables
Content-Type: application/json

### =====================================================
### 3. UNLINK COMPARABLE FROM APPRAISAL
### =====================================================

### 3.1 Unlink a comparable
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/appraisals/{{appraisalId}}/comparables/{{comparableId}}
Content-Type: application/json
